testCanMintMultipleReserved().notice: Test multiple reserved gobblers can be minted under fair circumstances.

testCanMintReserved().notice: Test that reserved gobblers can be minted under fair circumstances.

testCannotMintLegendaryWithLegendary().notice: Test that Legendary Gobblers can't be burned to mint another legendary.

testCannotRevealMoreGobblersThanRemainin.notice: Cannot reveal more gobblers than remaining to be revealed.

testCantAddMoreGooThanOwned().notice: Test that we can't add goo when we don't have the corresponding ERC20 balance.

testCantFeedArtToUnownedGobbler().notice: Test that you can't feed art to gobblers you don't own.

testCantFeedGobblers().notice: Test that gobblers can't eat other gobblers

testCantFeedUnownedArt().notice: Test that you can't feed art you don't own to your gobbler.

testCantMintTooFastReserved().notice: Test minting reserved gobblers fails if not enough have gobblers been minted.

testCantMintTooFastReservedOneByOne().notice: Test minting reserved gobblers fails one by one if not enough have gobblers been minted.

testCantRemoveGoo().notice: Test that goo can't be removed when the balance is insufficient.

testCantSetRandomSeedWithoutRevealing().notice: Test that seed can't be set without first revealing pending gobblers.

testDoesNotRevertEarly().notice: Pricing function should NOT revert when trying to price the last mintable gobbler.

testDoesRevertWhenExpected().notice: Pricing function should revert when trying to price beyond the last mintable gobbler.

testEmissionMultipleUpdatesAfterTransfer.notice: Test that emission multiple changes as expected after transfer.

testFeedingArt().notice: Test that pages can be fed to gobblers.

testGobblerBalancesAfterTransfer().notice: Test that gobbler balances are accurate after transfer.

testGooAddition().notice: Test that adding goo is reflected in balance.

testGooRemoval().notice: Test that goo removal works as expected.

testInitialGobblerPrice().notice: Test that initial gobbler price is what we expect.

testLegendaryGobblerFinalPrice().notice: Test that auction ends at a price of 0.

testLegendaryGobblerMidPrice().notice: Test that mid price happens when we expect.

testLegendaryGobblerMinStartPrice().notice: Test that target price does't fall below what we expect.

testLegendaryGobblerMintBeforeStart().notice: Test that attempting to mint before start time reverts.

testLegendaryGobblerPastFinalPrice().notice: Test that auction ends at a price of 0 even after the interval.

testLegendaryGobblerTargetPrice().notice: Test that Legendary Gobbler initial price is what we expect.

testLongRunningMintMaxFromGoo().notice: Check that max supply is mintable

testLongRunningMintMaxFromGooRevert().notice: Check that minting beyond max supply should revert.

testLongRunningMintMaxReserved().notice: Check that max reserved supplies are mintable.

testLongRunningMintMaxTeamRevert().notice: Check that minting reserves beyond their max supply reverts.

testMintFreeLegendaryGobbler().notice: Test that Legendary Gobblers can be minted at 0 cost.

testMintFreeLegendaryGobblerPastInterval.notice: Test that Legendary Gobblers can be minted at 0 cost.

testMintFromBalanceInsufficient().notice: Test that you can't mint with insufficient balance

testMintFromGoo().notice: Test that you can successfully mint from goo.

testMintFromGooBalance().notice: Test that you can successfully mint from goo.

testMintInsufficientBalance().notice: Test that trying to mint with insufficient balance reverts.

testMintLegendaryGobbler().notice: Test that Legendary Gobblers can be minted.

testMintLegendaryGobblerWithInsufficient.notice: Test that legendary gobblers can't be minted with insufficient payment.

testMintLegendaryGobblerWithSplippage().notice: Test that legendary gobblers can be minted with slippage.

testMintLegendaryGobblerWithUnownedId().notice: Test that legendary gobblers can't be minted if the user doesn't own one of the ids.

testMintLegendaryGobblersExpectedIds().notice: Test that legendary gobblers have expected ids.

testMintNotInMintlist().notice: Test that an invalid mintlist proof reverts.

testMintPriceExceededMax().notice: Test that if mint price exceeds max it reverts.

testMintReservedGobblersFailsWithNoMints.notice: Test that minting reserved gobblers fails if there are no mints.

testMintedLegendaryURI().notice: Test that legendary gobbler URI is correct.

testMintingFromMintlistTwiceFails().notice: Test that minting from the mintlist twice fails.

testMultiReveal().notice: Test that revevals work as expected

testPricingBasic().notice: Test VRGDA behavior when selling at target rate.

testRevealDelayInitialMint().notice: Cannot request random seed before 24 hours have passed from initial mint.

testRevealDelayRecurring().notice: Cannot request random seed before 24 hours have passed from last reveal,

testRevealedUri().notice: Test that revealed URI is correct.

testSimpleRewards().notice: test that goo balance grows as expected.

testSnapshotDoesNotAffectBalance().notice: make sure that actions that trigger balance snapshotting do not affect total balance.

testUnmintedLegendaryUri().notice: Test that un-minted legendary gobbler URI is correct.

testUnrevealedUri().notice: Test that unrevealed URI is correct.
